domain_knowledge.feature_meaning: Each attribute within the dataset has its significance: id - unique identifier, gender - Male or Female, age - patient's age, hypertension - having hypertension or not, heart_disease - having a heart disease or not, ever_married - married status, work_type - type of job, Residence_type - urban or rural residence, avg_glucose_level - average glucose level in blood, bmi - body mass index, smoking_status - smoking habits, stroke - having had a stroke or not
